      - Linux

      - CLI
      - GUI

      - Zero-configuration to get started
      - Multi-platform, multi-client: Windows, Mac, and Linux, CLI or app
      - Take your code anywhere: compile, publish, or wrap (Cordova, Electron)
      - Fast: incremental compiles on demand, don’t wait for your entire static site to rebuild
      - Secure: compiled content is static, published with HTTPS on harpjs.com domains

